        {
            "title": "新城廣播新春團拜丨張家輝現身撐場原來關馬浚偉事？ 鼓勵後輩最緊要全力付出 家燕姐聞俞明離世：難過又不捨",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"新城廣播新春團拜丨張家輝現身撐場原來關馬浚偉事？ 鼓勵後輩最緊要全力付出 家燕姐聞俞明離世：難過又不捨\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e8312cbc6049817a3b37eac6ce5d0799/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020617470314021.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">新城廣播新春團拜丨張家輝現身撐場原來關馬浚偉事？ 鼓勵後輩最緊要全力付出 家燕姐聞俞明離世：難過又不捨</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>張家輝、馬浚偉、薛家燕、吳若希等，今日（6日）出席新城廣播乙巳年新春團拜。最搞笑是家燕姐見到家輝即讚他越來越有型，家輝即謂家燕姐無皺紋又滑嘟嘟。家燕姐笑說：「我今朝拉咗面皮！」她又大讚家輝是後輩的學習對象，雖然未曾跟家輝合作，但見面都叫對方加油，但家輝說：「我想收油！」\n\n</p><h2>老友馬浚偉叫到很樂意參與</h2>\n<p>家輝表示與馬浚偉合作《妙手仁心》拍打籃球場口而熟落，所以老友叫到來參與很樂意，又笑指見到對方現在事業有成接受不來。談到可有鼓勵說話跟後輩說？家輝說：「有得做咪做囉！做好自己，努力工作，最緊要投入全力付出。」家燕姐提到在網上睇到家輝與容祖兒合唱片段，張家輝笑指被容祖兒傳染甲型流感，自己並沒有野心做歌星，但本身戲要人唱片尾歌，不過比人唱要畀錢人，所以咪自己搞。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"張家輝、馬浚偉、薛家燕等，今日（6日）出席新城廣播乙巳年新春團拜。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/74218d8301c319f4b0f616bfc0e6fac5/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張家輝、馬浚偉、薛家燕等，今日（6日）出席新城廣播乙巳年新春團拜。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家輝親自撐場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e7f4ef8966a17513dfa229a88586e8ee/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家輝親自撐場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家燕姐見到家輝即讚他有型，家輝即說家燕姐滑嘟嘟。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4cce9a2a927ec2081074bc71b1fe06f4/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家燕姐見到家輝即讚他有型，家輝即說家燕姐滑嘟嘟。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家燕姐又大讚家輝是後輩的學習對象！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a690e1a7e020851e2d748fc44cd505a2/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家燕姐又大讚家輝是後輩的學習對象！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家燕姐未曾跟家輝合作，但見到他想叫他加油，家輝笑說想收油！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cae8bb8a82186af9abcbc23b2fe3d044/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家燕姐未曾跟家輝合作，但見到他想叫他加油，家輝笑說想收油！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家輝的出現令大家都好開心。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8b89a7be8ebd6da6a9b55a8e68639c96/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家輝的出現令大家都好開心。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家輝表示與馬浚偉因合作《妙手仁心》而熟落。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0ef362a9ca068a7f3fc2b23fd32c6e7/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家輝表示與馬浚偉因合作《妙手仁心》而熟落。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家輝表示老友叫到好樂意參與。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/38fb3712a1eec9b208635b2283c567c6/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家輝表示老友叫到好樂意參與。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"原來2人因合作拍《妙手仁心》而熟絡。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/138d3d215c20505033083e268ea58fef/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        原來2人因合作拍《妙手仁心》而熟絡。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"張家輝、馬浚偉、薛家燕一起合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/019898e3f6ca04070404b8b191e45cd6/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_16.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張家輝、馬浚偉、薛家燕一起合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"談到可有鼓勵說話給後輩，家輝表示有得做咪做囉！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c5a11831a700b101824fb191af8e0838/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        談到可有鼓勵說話給後輩，家輝表示有得做咪做囉！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家輝指做好自己，最緊要投入全力付出。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b7fc32442e6df96846a24c2a61fbbaf/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_18.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家輝指做好自己，最緊要投入全力付出。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家燕姐在網上睇到家輝與容祖兒合唱片段，家輝笑指被容祖兒傳染甲型流感。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4af859043b96e9aab4e15f888f755873/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_20.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家燕姐在網上睇到家輝與容祖兒合唱片段，家輝笑指被容祖兒傳染甲型流感。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家燕姐見到家輝真係好開心。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f7a99ebb6b62fd9f78fdd84cebb20dbb/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_21.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家燕姐見到家輝真係好開心。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"馬浚偉、薛家燕\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1c1780aae90e482d021c314dd98adfc4/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161752527_22.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬浚偉、薛家燕\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>吳若希被問會否生蛇B：做乜咁睇唔開</h2>\n<p>吳若希表示在後台見到張家輝，大讚對方風趣幽默，還叫她不要鬧老公，但她會銘記於心，亦很愛老公，但今年已跟老公開年，並謂很想跟張家輝合唱，亦可跟家燕姐一齊跳十字步。談到可想生個蛇B增加家庭氣氛？她笑說：「做乜咁睇唔開呢，留返畀家燕姐再抱孫啦！」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家燕姐開心派利是。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a328f830634d27501871297a1484484d/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161941366_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家燕姐開心派利是。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家燕姐早有準備喎！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da2f0b0c49d041df08bfc830601d80a7/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161941366_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家燕姐早有準備喎！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家燕姐表示她心愛的孫仔已跟她拜年。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d87fd77857f96e3074b498ba8ab962e/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161941366_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家燕姐表示她心愛的孫仔已跟她拜年。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"對於粵語片笑匠俞明離世，家燕姐坦言難過又不捨。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e8f1c98923d82a65727e6dc7490234b/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161941366_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        對於粵語片笑匠俞明離世，家燕姐坦言難過又不捨。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"吳若希都有帶利是。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7601b3838aec7aee1c597c8974f2653b/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161941366_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        吳若希都有帶利是。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"吳若希在後台見到張家輝，大讚對方風趣幽默。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a19b79ac4387e23f96d5a6101bb5e9d3/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161941366_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        吳若希在後台見到張家輝，大讚對方風趣幽默。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"問到吳若希會否生蛇B，她表示做乜咁睇唔開。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/86c61856ba457f663a58de89da0f2e20/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_161941366_11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        問到吳若希會否生蛇B，她表示做乜咁睇唔開。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"粵語片笑匠俞明離世，享年100歲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a3b757ff8a9b542b5e170149c4141f1c/2025-02/D2X_0861.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        粵語片笑匠俞明離世，享年100歲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>家燕姐憶俞明叔講笑話𠱁自己</h2>\n<p>家燕姐則謂孫仔已跟她拜年，又爆孫仔見到她手持利是即以日文向她拜年，更透露農曆年一家人到日本旅行，雖然五點起身睇富士山，感覺舟車勞頓，但很享受。對於到粵語片笑匠俞明離世，享年100歲，家燕姐坦言雖然是笑喪，但也感到難過又不捨，又透露兒時拍戲，俞明叔見她瞌眼瞓就會講笑話𠱁她，帶給大家很多歡樂。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2051225/即時-娛樂-新城廣播新春團拜丨張家輝現身撐場原來關馬浚偉事-鼓勵後輩最緊要全力付出-家燕姐聞俞明離世-難過又不捨",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 17:56:01",
