        },
        {
            "title": "灣仔星域軒 時尚大廳典雅亮麗 擁小學12校網",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"灣仔星域軒 時尚大廳典雅亮麗 擁小學12校網\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f98c2f25c087806bc0cb0e63aacf812f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020617362353689.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">灣仔星域軒 時尚大廳典雅亮麗 擁小學12校網</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>灣仔星域軒是區內著名豪宅之一，鄰近港鐵金鐘站，又屬小學12校網。今日精選該屋苑2座高層A室，實用面積925方呎，採3房1套間隔，有豪華裝修及基本家具，最新以月租67,000元放租，實用呎租約72元。\n\n</p>\n<p>大廳整體以素色糅合木系設計作主題，配以大型深色沙發及茶几，迎合大玻璃窗採光引入市景。飯廳布置講究，放置了6人長形木餐桌，旁設落地玻璃鏡牆身，大大增強空間感。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4063417/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單位有3間房，所有房間間隔四正。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da8f9c276120ada1bb2f8e2c7bf09910/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_12_22_38_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單位有3間房，所有房間間隔四正。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4063418/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"飯廳放置了長形木餐桌，旁設落地玻璃鏡牆身，大大增強空間感。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4d161017975aa5ad89bb97ce2e727e42/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_12_22_40_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        飯廳放置了長形木餐桌，旁設落地玻璃鏡牆身，大大增強空間感。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4063419/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"圖中寢室空間闊落，靠牆有嵌入式衣櫃，善用空間。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0d369d18589c7e24e6c728bb49892177/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_12_22_42_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        圖中寢室空間闊落，靠牆有嵌入式衣櫃，善用空間。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4063420/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"灣仔星域軒2座高層A室，實用面積925方呎，最新月租叫價67000元。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dd044695f91856376186291818a6a484/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_12_22_45_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        灣仔星域軒2座高層A室，實用面積925方呎，最新月租叫價67000元。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4063426/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"星域軒外貌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c40e6743bcc3dc9f9176e32ac46cc8b4/2025-02/DPPG0324STARCREST024.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        星域軒外貌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>925呎3房1套間隔</h2>\n<p>來到睡房，放盤為3房1套間隔，當中主人套房中央設布大牀，可3邊上落大牀，靠牆有嵌入式衣櫃，善用空間。廚房空間寬敞，基本煮食設備齊全，加上設有轉角工作枱，更方便住客處理食材。\n\n</p>\n<p>由太古地產發展的星域軒，共設2座，提供超過320個單位，附設有戶外泳池、桌球房及健身室等設施。\n\n</p><h2>必睇靚位</h2>\n<p>鄰近港鐵金鐘站，又屬小學12校網\n\n</p>\n<p>3房1套設計\n\n</p>\n<p>豪華裝修及基本家具\n\n</p>\n<p>客廳設近落地窗，採光充足\n\n</p><h2>放租單位資料</h2>\n<p>物業名稱：星域軒\n\n</p>\n<p>地址：灣仔星街9號\n\n</p>\n<p>樓齡：24年\n\n</p>\n<p>單位：2座高層A室\n\n</p>\n<p>實用面積：925方呎\n\n</p>\n<p>間隔：3房1套\n\n</p>\n<p>叫租：67000元\n\n</p>\n<p>呎租：72元\n\n</p>\n<p>代理行：美聯物業\n\n</p>\n<p>電話：6097 2720(錢小姐)\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
